        T getConfig(@Nonnull
            String name,
            String fallbackName,
            @Nonnull
            ConfigSupplier<T> configSupplier)
        Get configuration for data structure with the given name
        Parameters:
        name - data structure name
        fallbackName - name to fallback if config for original name is not found
        configSupplier - data config supplier
        Returns:
        configuration for name or fallback config for fallbackName. If neither is found, null is returned.
